code: @Test public void defaultConfiguration() {     Long result = this.timeToLive.apply(EndpointId.of("test")).     assertThat(result).isNull(). }

@Test public void userConfiguration() {     this.environment.setProperty("management.endpoint.test.cache.time-to-live", "500").     Long result = this.timeToLive.apply(EndpointId.of("test")).     assertThat(result).isEqualTo(500L). }

@Test public void mixedCaseUserConfiguration() {     this.environment.setProperty("management.endpoint.another-test.cache.time-to-live", "500").     Long result = this.timeToLive.apply(EndpointId.of("anotherTest")).     assertThat(result).isEqualTo(500L). }
